<plot>Murder, it's far too often taken for granted, or feared or simply ignored. What motivates a man to kill? This is the question that drives Det. Danny Wilson and his novice partner Det. Monica Patterson, as they search for a man who acknowledges no law. There's only one problem, even if Wilson and his partner succeed, they still have to deal with the suspect's ace lawyer, Kevin Radner.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?412651</url></doc>
